        "timestamp": "2017-08-16 18:30:01.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\n> (1 comment)\n > \n > Testing in https://jenkins.onap.org/sandbox/job/appc-master-release-version-java-daily/\n > when job starts.\n\nNot sure if I'll be able to test this in sandbox. Having to modify appc-master-verify-java and it's still not working.\n\nIn build where sonar is not getting updated (https://logs.onap.org/production/vex-yul-ecomp-jenkins-1/appc-master-release-version-java-daily/171/console.log.gz) this appears to be the offending line:\n\"JaCoCoSensor: JaCoCo report not found : /w/workspace/appc-master-release-version-java-daily/appc-common/target/coverage-reports/jacoco.exec\"\n\nThis change removes the above path which appears to be wrong path since update to oparent as parent pom.xml (see https://git.onap.org/oparent/tree/pom.xml#n45 ) and replaces it with path that oparent pom.xml sets.",
        "patchset_number": 1
